{"tid":2185312,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大家返工有冇遇過咁痴撚線嘅人/事？","createTime":"2020-09-02T07:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T08:26:01.000Z","uid":24812,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"28731c58e7d508c8e3c7ead058a33ea057173332","tid":2185312,"uid":24812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人有呢單咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返過份工 入面有4成支那人<br />\n公司去廁所同出入要人面識別同拎鎖匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次去廁所 推開廁格門一行入去<br />\n見到個馬桶正面方地下有舊屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係圓圓扁扁有厚度有鞋印個隻 <br />\n好似撳扁左既屎色泥膠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n事後HR send咗 mass email 屌鬼<br />\n唔夠一個星期又有同事喺廁所見到屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係成舊個隻<br />\n不過今次係馬桶蓋同廁所板中間個骹位<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n清潔姐姐屌晒鬼之後冇再見到屎<br />\n但唔夠幾日<br />\n有人係廁所鎖匙牌上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到有撻屎跡<br />\nDKLM到依家都諗唔撚明條友點痾屎<br />\n<br />\n自此之後我每次去廁所都拎大量紙巾包住鎖匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />形住有支那屎味"},{"pid":"6c35233174ea5c3172c0cf53e8894f0b57454223","tid":2185312,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"你都會屙屎啦 體諒下啦"},{"pid":"e2f545f6405e85a7f6e0e097d1f251ee82c4fedc","tid":2185312,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"我係你我寧可去附近大商場屙好過<br />\nbtw有支那人嘅地方就會有屎坑俾人強姦"},{"pid":"5b3caa1d9b5dc8145c832c4477a2388f4f1d0ab5","tid":2185312,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"日日著同一件衫"},{"pid":"770789f831a229c3d7bb6eaff2433961398e58d4","tid":2185312,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"試過一開廁所門見到舊屎係屎坑 , 無用廁紙 , 乜柒都無"},{"pid":"d06d7b781b16953043552e2530ec18c459c016b8","tid":2185312,"uid":24812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c35233174ea5c3172c0cf53e8894f0b57454223","tid":2185312,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"你都會屙屎啦 體諒下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"就算企上廁板痾都唔會痾到去前面掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點做到"},{"pid":"f5e9b4b42c171adaf472a99a7861206dba2661ea","tid":2185312,"uid":50502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"有人面識別但捉唔到邊個屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814dfe98a5f1b8b069ebac7f4f2f6e22f6cd48d8","tid":2185312,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"},{"pid":"7f0e75a79d79ca54f697035ff7a0acf307fef4b9","tid":2185312,"uid":320293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a60f0e47250ad9648419d11141273d3f3443416","tid":2185312,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f0e75a79d79ca54f697035ff7a0acf307fef4b9","tid":2185312,"uid":320293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b3caa1d9b5dc8145c832c4477a2388f4f1d0ab5","tid":2185312,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"日日著同一件衫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"IT狗黎"},{"pid":"5270894fe1fb44e48ce00ba029279debf2ad45ae","tid":2185312,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"偷影女同事斷正"},{"pid":"6cc26f04c6da1930c0c7a0f2b40dca53cef0ca4b","tid":2185312,"uid":197584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"支那人屙屎真係估你唔到<br />\n啲屎成日出現喺唔同地方<br />\n總之佢地就唔會正正常常屙完舊屎沖走佢<br />\n硬係要搞到周圍污糟哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ea1d4d56f730deb260db60ba543d64082a3fbb","tid":2185312,"uid":24812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e9b4b42c171adaf472a99a7861206dba2661ea","tid":2185312,"uid":50502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"有人面識別但捉唔到邊個屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"入面冇ga嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通驗d屎對樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享多單 出入同去廁所都要face id 都on9<br />\n最煩係成撚日detect唔到 再加上呢排肺炎次次都要拉低個口罩落黎<br />\n<br />\n個on9老細之前請左個人返黎<br />\n每日淨係負責數每個同事去咗幾多次廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n老細又鍾意臨放工先叫人開會 已經仆街架啦<br />\n7點放工 6點半叫人等佢一陣 有野想傾<br />\n一等等撚到9點佢開完會出黎 <br />\n問人做咩仲係度等 叫人快D走今日唔傾住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n全公司貼晒咩主席綱領<br />\n咩以公司利益大於個人 不要煽動仇恨情緒<br />\n同某個國家好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好撚多on9野"},{"pid":"684e1a512c0601d21d83015d1e456a1ff241507e","tid":2185312,"uid":24812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cc26f04c6da1930c0c7a0f2b40dca53cef0ca4b","tid":2185312,"uid":197584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"支那人屙屎真係估你唔到<br />\n啲屎成日出現喺唔同地方<br />\n總之佢地就唔會正正常常屙完舊屎沖走佢<br />\n硬係要搞到周圍污糟哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"佢地好似唔知d屎係要痾落個窿到咁<br />\n仲咗馬桶入面其他位都有屎出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd824ffb969a69d131c1c82ed0018aee45b8f5de","tid":2185312,"uid":12348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"當年返餐廳長炒，同嗰經理吹水，傾無聊野講話用水烚熟食物營養成分會唔會流失左。<br />\n我覺得會流失嘅，經理持相反意見。爭論左五分鐘，我就自己google俾經理睇，搜尋結果係有部分食物的確會因為烚熟嘅過程流失營養成分。<br />\n但個經理仲不停咁jer住我話「梗係唔係！」「啲後生真係唔聽人講嘢」，大聲到廚房都聽到（嗰日無乜客）<br />\n我同佢講，傾無聊野都可以咁燥做乜嘢。跟住就行開唔理佢，佢好似有燥狂症咁仲喺度咿咿吟吟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"814dfe98a5f1b8b069ebac7f4f2f6e22f6cd48d8","tid":2185312,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"}}